            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost">P</supplied>agani pagi Lucreti qui sunt fini<lb break="no" n="2"/>bus Arelatensium loco Gargario <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cor</abbr><ex>nelio</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Marcelli <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>erto</ex></expan> Zosimo <expan><abbr>IIIIIIvir</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustali</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>onia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Paterna Arelate ob honorem eius qui notum <note>sic</note> fecit <lb n="5"/>iniuriam nostram omnium saec<supplied reason="lost">ulor</supplied>um sacra<lb break="no" n="6"/>tissimo principi <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> Aelio Antonino <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> Pio te</supplied>r Romae <lb n="7"/>misit per multos annos ad praesides p<supplied reason="lost">rovinci</supplied>ae perse<lb break="no" n="8"/>cutus est iniuriam nostram suis in<supplied reason="lost">pensis e</supplied>t ob hoc <lb n="9"/>donavit nobis inpendia quae fecit ut omnium saecu<lb break="no" n="10"/>lorum sacratissimi principis <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>aris</ex></expan> Antonini <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> Pii <lb n="11"/>beneficia durarent permanerentque quibus frueremur <lb n="12"/><supplied reason="lost">aquis</supplied> et balineo gratuito quod ablatum erat paganis <lb n="13"/>quod usi fuerant amplius annis XXXX
            </ab></div>
